tip.text: The oldest bar in Glasgow and you can feel it! No one is in a rush in this cozy bar with a great atmosphere.
A lovely cafe with great coffee, food and service! Could be a bit more roomy though.
A cozy pub with nice location and super friendly staff! Food was ok too.
Falafel is great! Kebab pretty much average.
One of the best pizzas ever! And super friendly service. 5/5
